ItemizedList.ListItem:
In stage IIA:no tumor is found in the breast, but cancer is found in the axillary lymph nodes (lymph nodes under the arm);
				orthe tumor is 2 centimeters or smaller and has spread
				to the axillary lymph nodes;
				or 
			 the tumor is larger than 2 centimeters but not larger than 5 centimeters and has not
				spread to the axillary lymph nodes.
